"vindalu", ek Goenchea jevnna khannacho  promannacho ghottok asa zo Purtugez carne de vinha d'alhos (utram pormonnem "losunnachea sorean buddovn kelolo"),ek masacho prat (chodd korun dukrachea masacho) zo sorean ani losunnant buddovn kelolo asta..[2] Mull Purtugez prat, Purtugez tarvotti koch’che jinos lakddachea bol’lamni dukrachem mas ani losunn "samballun" dovortalet zaka soreant buddovpant ietalem. Hachem thollavea Goenkar kuzneramni "Bharotikoronn" kelem zantunt  tambddea sorea suvater tannim maddanchi vinagr, vaporli ani sukeo tambddeo mirsango odik mosaleant zoddleo.To magir thollavo zavn “vindalu:  uchharunk sompo zalo[4]Halincheatempar, Britix Asiachea prokarachea vindalucho masant vinagrt, sakhort, tajema alem ani mosalo ratbhor buddovn odik mosalo ghalun randpant ieta.

== Bharoti pod’dhotin toiari ani veglleponn ==
Goenchm  hottelam jim Goenchem jevonn khann bhettoitat  tim dukrachea masa sangata vindalu ditat ji os’sol randpachi rit zavn asa. Goenkar kuzneramni ( zankam Brittix posont kortalet, kiteak tankam kuznant ani baramni gaichem mas, dukrachem mas vo soro hatallunk prosn naslo) ho  prat Britix sonsthamni ani doreant choltolea agbottimni famad kelo. Goeam bhair hottelam vindalu kombie masa vo bokddeachea masa sangata ditat zantunt ken’nai bottate bhorxitat.Zorui alu utor Hindint bottatto, paromporik vindalunt bottate nastat.

== Bharota bhair ==
Bharota bhair Vindalu famad zalo, ani sonvsar bhor Bharoti hottelamni to jevnna vollerint dista. Zo United Kingdom hanga divpant ieta to vindalu os’sol vindalu poros vegllo; to ek chodd tikhott promann “modheom (tikhott)” hottelanchi koddi zantunt odik vinagr, bottatte ani mirsango astat..[6]  Britix veglleponn Brittix Bangladexi 1970 vorsantlea hottelam koddlean ailam.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://andyskitchen.co.uk/blogs////blog1.php/recipes/lamb-phall-vindaloo-and-madras-curry-recipe-1-recipe-three-different-curries|title=lamb phall,vindaloo and madras curry recipes|website=andyskitchen.co.uk|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027231826/http://andyskitchen.co.uk/blogs////blog1.php/recipes/lamb-phall-vindaloo-and-madras-curry-recipe-1-recipe-three-different-curries|archive-date=27 October 2017|dead-url=no|access-date=9 May 2018}}</ref>

Vindalu ek tikhott prat jevnna vollericho zoim to divpant ieta, zorui hottelam tindaloo ditat zo ek prat Bangladesant oromb ghetlolea poros vegllo zavn asa.

